@startuml
title Admin visibility

actor Admin
participant "NewsCrudController" as NewsCrud
participant "NewsExportCrudController" as ExportCrud
participant "NewsExportStarter" as Starter
database "NewsExport" as Export
database "MessengerBatch" as Batch

Admin -> NewsCrud: start export selected/all
NewsCrud -> Starter: start(ids)
Starter -> Export: create export journal record
Starter -> Batch: create and start batch

Admin -> ExportCrud: open exports list
ExportCrud -> Export: load export records
ExportCrud -> Batch: show linked batch status/counters
ExportCrud --> Admin: status + final file path

@enduml
